{{Databox|en=Siwi language}}'''Awal n isiwan''' nɣ d '''jlan n isiwan''' (s wawal n isiwan) nɣ daɣ '''tasiwiyt''', iga [[tutlayt tamaziɣt]] ittyusawaln ɣ [[isiwan]], ula d [[gaṛa]], sin id wazis llanin ɣ tagut n [[Miṣra|Miẓṛa]], aẓn i iwtta nns d [[libya]]. ngr 15,000 d 20,000 n middn ad tt isawaln.

tga tsiwiyt tutlayt n umyawaḍ akuyass ɣ dar imaziɣn imisṛiyn n siwa d gaṛa.

